name: MisMizery // BE
description: Don’t condemn yourself to society’s ideals. You don’t have to choose and live in the confusion, you can be all of it. Let your inner self see the light.  BE – Static Digital Editions.  The signature MisMizery heart finds its way into a hand-illustrated mixed digital media piece. The first of MisMizery’s collection to primarily feature illustration. ‘BE’ was minted Saturday April 24th, 3:10pm EST. Animated avail on Opensea. Physical copies of this piece will also be released at mismizery.co
